						<summary>

						<p>This is a mere fragment of an inscription which seems to record a gift of money for burning a lamp in the temple, by a resident of Karuppūr in Miṟaikkūṟṟam who left it in charge of the <hi rend="italic">Nagarattār</hi> of Vāḷaiyūr.</p>						

